  <section id="overview">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Program Overview</h2>
      <p>Our Travel ER Doctor Program connects experienced ER veterinarians with relief shifts across VCA hospitals. Whether you're seeking variety, extra income, or to help where it's needed most, this program offers flexibility and comprehensive support.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="benefits">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Compensation & Benefits</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Compensation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>10 shifts per 4-week period: $200,000 annually</li>
            <li>12 shifts per 4-week period: $230,000 annually</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>PTO & CE</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Vacation: 2 weeks standard</li>
            <li>Sick Days: 5 days</li>
            <li>CE: $3,000 + 1 week (40 hours) CE time off</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Licensure</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Reimbursement for DEA & initial two state license fees</li>
            <li>Additional state licensure reimbursement available with a commitment of 12 shifts over 2–3 assignment periods</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="logistics">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Travel Logistics & Perks</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Ground Travel</h3>
          <p>Reimbursed mileage if within a 4-hour drive; flights covered for distances over 4 hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Accommodations</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Hotel night before if shift begins before 2pm</li>
            <li>Hotel night after if shift ends after 2pm</li>
            <li>Rental car expensed with prior approval</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Shift Requirements & Perks</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Minimum of 3 consecutive shifts for air travel bookings</li>
            <li>Corporate AMEX card provided for travel arrangements—keep all reward points</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="onboarding">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Onboarding</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Dedicated Program Director</strong> to guide you at every step of your travel journey</li>
        <li><strong>WOOFware Training</strong> – 2 days of comprehensive system onboarding</li>
        <li><strong>Shadow Shift</strong> at a new hospital to gain hands-on familiarity before your first independent shift (counts as one shift toward your required period total)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

